		@ 7,2  say "บ Use PgUp to page up                 Use PgDn to page down             บ "
		@ 8,2  say "บ Use Ctrl-PgUp to go to letter start Use Ctrl-PgDn to go to letter end บ "
		@ 9,2  say "บ Use Home to move to start of line   Use End to move to end of line    บ "
		@ 10,2 say "บ Use Ctrl-Home to move top of page   Use Ctrl-End to move end of page  บ "
		@ 11,2 say "บ Use Del to delete right             Use Backspace to delete left      บ "
		@ 12,2 say "บ Use Insert to toggle insert mode    Use Alt-P to print letter         บ "
		@ 13,2 say "บ Use Alt-R to delete line            Use Alt-I to insert line          บ "
		@ 14,2 say "บ Use Alt-T to toggle word wrap       Use Alt-M to set margins          บ "
		@ 15,2 say "บ Use Alt-U to update (search & rep.) Use Alt-S to search               บ "
